          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>Given any set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, there does not exist a function <fr:link href="/forest/000R/" title="One-to-One and Onto" uri="https://andrewczezowski.github.io/forest/000R/" display-uri="000R" type="local">1-1 and onto</fr:link> that maps <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f:A\rightarrow  P(A)]]></fr:tex>. Where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[P(A)]]></fr:tex> is the <fr:link href="/forest/000T/" title="Power Sets" uri="https://andrewczezowski.github.io/forest/000T/" display-uri="000T" type="local">power set</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
